{"tid":826434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【消委會】小米1,099元空氣淨化機 表現勝5,480元Dyson機","createTime":"2018-09-18T08:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T10:10:38.000Z","uid":54870,"like":43,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0807f1281106cf60a6bd7f73a972535762cf1022","tid":826434,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:44:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180918/58694442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58694442&d=g7k2Ncn0pY6isMlTzy50xdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=805466cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58694442&h=3e5a45e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180918/58694442</a><br />\n<br />\n消委會測試12款空氣清新機，發現樣本於去除香煙煙霧、塵埃及花粉的速度參差，去除甲醛的速度尤其懸殊，當中2款樣本整體表現突出，而1款約$1,100的樣本的空氣淨化速度以至整體表現，更勝2款5千多元的樣本。<br />\n12樣本中售價最低的「小米Xiaomi」空氣淨化器2S(1,099元)，量得除甲醛CADR為34.8立方呎/分鐘，在全部樣本中排第2位，其除顆粒物的速度亦不俗，獲4分；量得除煙霧、塵埃及花粉的CADR分別為166.9立方呎/分鐘、163.1立方呎/分鐘、119.7立方呎/分鐘，空氣淨化表現為3.5分，整體總評分為4分(最高為5分)。<br />\n至於樣本中2款「Dyson」空氣淨化器Pure Cool TP04及Pure Cool Link TP03(同為5,480元)，量得除煙霧、塵埃及花粉的CADR分別為79.8及59.9立方呎/分鐘、81.8及64.0立方呎/分鐘，以及99.8及48.6立方呎/分鐘，評分只有3分及2.5分，兩者空氣淨化表現分別只有3分及2.5分，兩者整體總評分為3分。<br />\n樣本中最貴的Blueair Classic 405(Smoke Stop)(7,080元)，整體表現亦不及「小米Xiaomi」，總評分只有3.5分，但空氣淨化表現一樣有3.5分，而其除顆粒物的速度就較好，有4.5分。<br />\n<br />\n潔淨空氣量（Clean Air Delivery Rate，CADR）是反映空氣淨化機的淨化能力的參數，指的是空氣淨化機提供不含特定污染物的空氣的速度，數值愈高，表示淨化該污染物的速度愈快，淨化能力愈好。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買小米(1,099元)：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買Dyson(5,480元)：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a63948ead870389ffa51b1bf6cea6c8e14f0203","tid":826434,"uid":88737,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:59:48.000Z","msg":"Dyson 果部係風扇黎 空氣淨化係額外功能<br />\n<br />\n如果塵網太密會影響番主要風扇既功能"},{"pid":"5ca985018bb11490f0fe57a812c2a5a2329d69f9","tid":826434,"uid":60628,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"之後就會揭發消委會自己買 Dyson"},{"pid":"8c1102d8a3b6a1c9a458b5e8a3fabf0104439bca","tid":826434,"uid":103230,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:01:30.000Z","msg":"消委會試過部機幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n大陸野不嬲都出名快壞"},{"pid":"f25a671443fbd0c887adfdbc23ab274d18eb7220","tid":826434,"uid":34223,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"俾千一蚊買個炸彈返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76eef10dcc231837150b33c3b9330c5f71e2b77","tid":826434,"uid":122885,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母拎部純種空氣清新機同部有空氣清新功能嘅風扇嚟比？"},{"pid":"cf4a9b022911e845ca7e1df7ed2d798612fd8acf","tid":826434,"uid":17857,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"有新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎風扇同空氣清新機嚟比，下次可以試下冷氣機鬥浴室寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac8a4cfba6f513e6739c6a1eebf9e0294775bfd","tid":826434,"uid":74935,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"兩部都唔買<br />\n買sharp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829008e7eca7cc1ea71b6106e8843cb7c38e2d3c","tid":826434,"uid":198797,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"但消委會無測試埋兩者既容易起火程度"},{"pid":"42e447ceb4bfb4b17b1cc0ed80dff31dda6f3016","tid":826434,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T23:40:46.000Z","msg":"dyson貴在個摩打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n濾得好但唔襟用又如何？"},{"pid":"04bdcf12911ecd3024048d1106c630a8a71ac269","tid":826434,"uid":389,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"5