Time":"2018-09-19T00:56:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/236995/%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E8%B2%B4%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E5%B9%B3%E6%A9%9F-dyson%E6%89%B9%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E9%81%8E%E6%BF%BE%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F236995%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E6%25A9%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25A9%259F-dyson%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2598%25A0%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25BF%25BE%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%25B4%25A0&d=g7k2Ncn0pY6isMlTzy50xdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ae2b0a14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/236995/%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E8%B2%B4%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E5%B9%B3%E6%A9%9F-dyson%E6%89%B9%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E9%81%8E%E6%BF%BE%E8%B3%AA%E7%B4%A0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"吊，Dyson 呢d得個樣嘅仆街又係掙唔落<br />\n<br />\n發言人指出，消委會所測試的潔淨空氣量（CADR）是其中一個廣為應用的測試標準，惟Dyson較着重於為實際家居提供高質量、均勻的淨化空氣，故於今年年初，與國家級測試機構<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國家用電器研究院</span>(CHEARI) ，首創更貼近實際生活環境的測試方法「 POLAR測試」 (Point Loading Automated Response)，在290平方呎的房間測試機器，顯示其空氣淨化風扇適用於淨化現實房間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97091b6d44a127aa309753d7af22f398eadb5ef7","tid":826434,"uid":193131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"消委會次次測試都講明會考慮埋價錢，咁中國果堆用黑錢頂爛市的產品好難唔贏，同埋唔耐用就test 唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}